{% comment %}
  Renders product variant-picker (Split Variant Version)
  针对单属性（颜色）拆分产品设计的定制版本
{% endcomment %}

{%- liquid 
  # 获取当前产品的系列元字段（请确保在 Shopify 后台定义了 custom.product_family）
  assign product_family = product.metafields.custom.product_family.value 
-%}

<div class="product-variant-picker-wrapper">
  {%- if product_family and product_family.members.value.size > 1 -%}
    <div class="product-form__input" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <legend class="form__label" style="font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.3rem;">
        Select Color
      </legend>
      
      <div class="swatch-container">
        {%- for sibling in product_family.members.value -%}
          {%- liquid
            # 获取色卡图片：优先取元字段自定义图片，没有则取产品主图
            assign texture_img = sibling.metafields.custom.swatch_image.value
            assign is_current = false
            if sibling.id == product.id
              assign is_current = true
            endif
          -%}
          
          <a href="{{ sibling.url }}" 
             class="swatch-link {% if is_current %}is-active{% endif %}"
             title="{{ sibling.title }}">
            <div class="swatch-image-wrapper">
              {%- if texture_img != blank -%}
                <img src="{{ texture_img | image_url: width: 100, height: 100, crop: 'center' }}" alt="{{ sibling.title }}" loading="lazy">
              {%- else -%}
                <img src="{{ sibling.featured_image | image_url: width: 100, height: 100, crop: 'center' }}" alt="{{ sibling.title }}" loading="lazy">
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          </a>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- comment -%}
    由于是拆分产品，每个产品只有一个默认变体或唯一的颜色变体。
    我们隐藏原生选择器，但保留隐藏的 Input 确保加购功能正常。
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}" form="{{ product_form_id }}">
</div>

<style>
  .swatch-container {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  
  .swatch-link {
    width: 4.5rem;
    height: 4.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding: 2px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    display: block;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  
  .swatch-image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: #f7f7f7;
  }
  
  .swatch-image-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .swatch-link:hover {
    border-color: #000;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .swatch-link.is-active {
    border: 2px solid #000 !important;
    transform: scale(1.1);
    pointer-events: none; /* 当前产品禁止重复点击 */
  }

  /* 隐藏原生可能存在的任何多属性选项 */
  variant-radios, variant-selects, variant-color {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>

{%- comment -%}
  如果该网站有 AJAX 加购逻辑，
  保留以下脚本以确保加购按钮在页面加载时处于可用状态。
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.addEventListener('load', function() {
    const atcButton = document.querySelector('button[name="add"]');
    if (atcButton) {
      atcButton.removeAttribute('disabled');
      atcButton.classList.remove('disabled');
    }
  });
</script>